---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="FILM" description="SAGE Anomaly — the AI film. Coming soon.">
  <div class="movie-layout">
    <div class="movie-bg">
      <img src="/images/002_AnomalyAttacksGlitchOpti.gif" alt="" aria-hidden="true" />
    </div>
    <div class="movie-content">
      <div class="transmission-header">
        <span class="tx">// INCOMING SIGNAL</span>
        <div class="signal-bars">
          <span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h1>THE<br/><span class="h1-accent">ENTITY</span><br/>FILM</h1>

      <div class="status-block">
        <div class="status-row">
          <span class="sk">PROJECT STATUS</span>
          <span class="sv sv-warn">IN DEVELOPMENT</span>
        </div>
        <div class="status-row">
          <span class="sk">MEDIUM</span>
          <span class="sv">AI-GENERATED FILM</span>
        </div>
        <div class="status-row">
          <span class="sk">RELEASE</span>
          <span class="sv">TBA</span>
        </div>
        <div class="status-row">
          <span class="sk">BASED ON</span>
          <span class="sv">SAGE ANOMALY NOVEL</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="movie-desc">
        The SAGE Anomaly story is being developed as an AI-generated film.
        The Entity's visual language — oscilloscope art processed through GAN models —
        will form the visual backbone of a feature-length narrative.
      </p>

      <p class="movie-desc">
        Early footage from the Vimeo channel shows what the film will look like.
        New material released as chapters are completed.
      </p>

      <div class="ctas">
        <a href="https://vimeo.com/479329386" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn-primary">
          Watch Early Footage on Vimeo ↗
        </a>
        <a href="/story" class="btn-ghost">Read the Story First</a>
      </div>

      <div class="notify-block">
        <p class="notify-label">// STAY UPDATED</p>
        <p>Follow the project on Async.art and SuperRare for film release announcements.</p>
        <div class="notify-links">
          <a href="https://async.art/v2/482?referrer=masters" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Async.art ↗</a>
          <a href="https://superrare.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">SuperRare ↗</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .movie-layout {
    min-height: calc(100vh - 140px);
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .movie-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .movie-bg img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    opacity: 0.08;
    filter: hue-rotate(100deg) saturate(1.5);
  }

  .movie-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    max-width: 700px;
    padding: 6rem 2rem;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .transmission-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .tx {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--green);
    letter-spacing: 0.25em;
  }

  .signal-bars {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-end;
    gap: 3px;
    height: 20px;
  }

  .signal-bars span {
    width: 3px;
    background: var(--green);
    opacity: 0.6;
    animation: bar-pulse 1.2s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  .signal-bars span:nth-child(1) { height: 30%; animation-delay: 0s; }
  .signal-bars span:nth-child(2) { height: 55%; animation-delay: 0.1s; }
  .signal-bars span:nth-child(3) { height: 80%; animation-delay: 0.2s; }
  .signal-bars span:nth-child(4) { height: 55%; animation-delay: 0.3s; }
  .signal-bars span:nth-child(5) { height: 30%; animation-delay: 0.4s; }

  @keyframes bar-pulse {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 0.3; }
    50% { opacity: 1; }
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 6rem);
    line-height: 0.9;
    color: var(--text);
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .h1-accent { color: var(--green); text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,255,65,0.4); }

  .status-block {
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 0;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .status-row {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 0.65rem 1rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }

  .status-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

  .sk { color: var(--muted); }
  .sv { color: var(--text); }
  .sv-warn { color: var(--amber); }

  .movie-desc {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.85;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .ctas {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--green);
    color: #000;
    padding: 0.7rem 1.5rem;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.2s;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--amber); color: #000; }

  .btn-ghost {
    border: 1px solid var(--muted);
    color: var(--text);
    padding: 0.7rem 1.5rem;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-decoration: none;
    display: inline-block;
    transition: border-color 0.2s, color 0.2s;
  }

  .btn-ghost:hover { border-color: var(--green); color: var(--green); }

  .notify-block {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding-top: 2rem;
  }

  .notify-label {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .notify-block > p {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .notify-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .notify-links a {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--green);
    text-decoration: none;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
  }

  .notify-links a:hover { border-color: var(--green); }
</style>
